{
  "screen_id": "qr-resume",
  "route": "/qr/resume",
  "title": "観測を再開する",
  "layout": "standard",
  "notes": "wave1-obs R1(QR→観測の最短導線): /qr/{token} の3解決(個体QR/棚QR占有/棚QR空)を画面側で分岐(observation-routes.ts GET /qr/:token)。空の棚(entry_mode=qr_placement_empty・individual_id:null)は『個体が見つかりました』と偽らず新規個体登録へ導く(旧: resumeボタンがid=nullで追観測へ死路になっていた・OBS目的宣言『最少クリックで記録』の綻び)。分岐はrenderer props.when(eq/not_eq・NodeView先頭で全ノード評価)のみで表現し、schemas/・renderer.tsx・共有物は無改変。占有パスの文言(個体が見つかりました/個体 ID:/この個体で観測を続ける)は既存E2E(observation.spec §7-8)の資産のため不変で維持。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "shell",
      "type": "app-shell",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "page",
          "type": "page",
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "title-found",
              "type": "heading",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.title.text",
                "text": "個体が見つかりました",
                "level": 1,
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "title-empty",
              "type": "heading",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.title-empty.text",
                "text": "空の棚です",
                "level": 1,
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "lead-found",
              "type": "text",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.lead.text",
                "text": "この個体の文脈で、前回値を引き継いで観測を続けます。",
                "muted": true,
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "lead-empty",
              "type": "text",
              "props": {
                "text_key": "qr-resume.lead-empty.text",
                "text": "この棚にはまだ個体がいません。この棚で新規個体を登録できます。",
                "muted": true,
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "resolve",
              "type": "card",
              "props": { "source_path": "/api/v1/qr/{{params.token}}?prefill=1" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "ind-id",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text_key": "qr-resume.ind-id.text",
                    "text": "個体 ID: {{data.resolve.individual_id}}",
                    "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "prefill-species",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text_key": "qr-resume.prefill-species.text",
                    "text": "前回の種の候補: {{data.resolve.prefill.species_candidate}}",
                    "muted": true,
                    "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "placement-id",
                  "type": "text",
                  "props": {
                    "text_key": "qr-resume.placement-id.text",
                    "text": "棚 ID: {{data.resolve.placement_id}}",
                    "muted": true,
                    "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "resume",
              "type": "button",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.resume.label",
                "label": "この個体で観測を続ける",
                "variant": "primary",
                "when": { "not_eq": ["{{data.resolve.individual_id}}", ""] }
              },
              "action": { "kind": "navigate", "to": "obs-register-entry?id={{data.resolve.individual_id}}" }
            },
            {
              "id": "resume-new",
              "type": "button",
              "props": {
                "label_key": "qr-resume.resume-new.label",
                "label": "この棚で新規個体を登録",
                "variant": "primary",
                "when": { "eq": ["{{data.resolve.entry_mode}}", "qr_placement_empty"] }
              },
              "action": { "kind": "navigate", "to": "obs-register-new" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "transitions": [
    { "from": "resume", "to_screen_id": "obs-register-entry", "label": "個体文脈付きで観測入力へ(OBS-25正本フロー)" },
    { "from": "resume-new", "to_screen_id": "obs-register-new", "label": "空の棚から新規個体登録へ" }
  ]
}
